1.  package com.msb.dao.impl;
2.  import com.msb.dao.StudentDao;
3.  import com.msb.pojo.Student;
4.  import java.util.List;
5.  /**
6.   * @Author: Ma HaiYang
7.   * @Description: MircoMessage:Mark_7001
8.   */
9.  public class StudentDaoImpl extends BaseDao implements StudentDao {
10.     @Override
11.     public List<Student> findByPage(String stuname,String stuage,int
    currentPage, int pageSize) {
12.         StringBuilder sql=new StringBuilder("select  * from student where
    1=1 ");
13.         if(null != stuname && !"".equals(stuname)) {
14.             sql.append("and stuname like ? ");
15.         }
16.         if(null != stuage && !"".equals(stuage)) {
17.             sql.append("and stuage > ? ");
18.         }
19.         sql.append("limit ?,?");
20.         System.out.println(sql.toString());
21.         List list =null;
22.         if(null != stuname && !"".equals(stuname) && null != stuage &&
    !"".equals(stuage)){
23.              list = baseQuery(Student.class, sql.toString(),
    "%"+stuname+"%",stuage,(currentPage - 1) * pageSize, pageSize);
24.         }else if ((null != stuname && !"".equals(stuname)) && (null ==
    stuage || "".equals(stuage))){
25.              list = baseQuery(Student.class, sql.toString(),
    "%"+stuname+"%",(currentPage - 1) * pageSize, pageSize);
26.         }else if ((null == stuname || "".equals(stuname))&& (null != stuage
    && !"".equals(stuage))){
27.              list = baseQuery(Student.class, sql.toString(),
    stuage,(currentPage - 1) * pageSize, pageSize);
28.         }else{
29.              list = baseQuery(Student.class, sql.toString(), (currentPage -
    1) * pageSize, pageSize);
30.         }
31.         return list;
32.     }
33.     @Override
34.     public int findTotalSize(String stuname,String stuage) {
35.         StringBuilder sql=new StringBuilder("select  count(1) from student
    where 1=1 ");
36.         if(null != stuname && !"".equals(stuname)) {
37.             sql.append("and stuname like ? ");
38.         }
39.         if(null != stuage && !"".equals(stuage)) {
40.             sql.append("and stuage > ? ");
41.         }
42.         int count =0;
43.         if(null != stuname && !"".equals(stuname) && null != stuage &&
    !"".equals(stuage)){
44.             count = baseQueryInt( sql.toString(), "%"+stuname+"%",stuage);
45.         }else if ((null != stuname && !"".equals(stuname)) && (null ==
    stuage || "".equals(stuage))){
46.             count = baseQueryInt( sql.toString(), "%"+stuname+"%");
47.         }else if ((null == stuname || "".equals(stuname))&& (null != stuage
    && !"".equals(stuage))){
48.             count = baseQueryInt( sql.toString(),stuage);
49.         }else{
50.             count = baseQueryInt(sql.toString());
51.         }
52.         return count;
53.     }
54. }

 




service层代码 




1.  package com.msb.service.impl;
2.  import com.msb.dao.StudentDao;
3.  import com.msb.dao.impl.StudentDaoImpl;
4.  import com.msb.pojo.PageBean;
5.  import com.msb.pojo.Student;
6.  import com.msb.service.StudentService;
7.  import java.util.List;
8.  /**
9.   * @Author: Ma HaiYang
10.  * @Description: MircoMessage:Mark_7001
11.  */
12. public class StudentServiceImpl implements StudentService {
13.     private StudentDao studentDao =new StudentDaoImpl();
14.     // 做分页数据封装的业务处理
15.     @Override
16.     public PageBean<Student> findByPage(String stuname,String stuage,int
    currentPage, int pageSize) {
17.         // 查询出该页所有数据
18.         List<Student> students = studentDao.findByPage( stuname,
    stuage,currentPage, pageSize);
19.         // 查询出有多少条数据
20.         int totalSize =studentDao.findTotalSize( stuname, stuage);
21.         // 总页数
22.         int totalPage
    =totalSize%pageSize==0?totalSize/pageSize:totalSize/pageSize+1;
23.         // 当前页
24.         // 页大小
25.         PageBean<Student> pageBean =new PageBean<>(students,  totalSize, 
    pageSize,  totalPage,  currentPage);
26.         return pageBean;
27.     }
28. }

 




controller层代码 




1.  package com.msb.controller;
2.  import com.msb.pojo.PageBean;
3.  import com.msb.pojo.Student;
4.  import com.msb.service.StudentService;
5.  import com.msb.service.impl.StudentServiceImpl;
6.  import javax.servlet.ServletException;
7.  import javax.servlet.annotation.WebServlet;
8.  import javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet;
9.  import javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest;
10. import javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse;
11. import java.io.IOException;
12. /**
13.  * @Author: Ma HaiYang
14.  * @Description: MircoMessage:Mark_7001
15.  */
16. @WebServlet(urlPatterns = "/showStudentController.do")
17. public class ShowStudentController extends HttpServlet {
18.     private StudentService studentService=new StudentServiceImpl();
19.     @Override
20.     protected void service(HttpServletRequest req, HttpServletResponse
    resp) throws ServletException, IOException {
21.         // 接收数据
22.         // 页码数
23.         int currentPage =1;
24.         try {
25.             currentPage=Integer.parseInt(req.getParameter("currentPage"));
26.         } catch (NumberFormatException e) {
27.         }
28.         // 页大小
29.         int pageSize =5;
30.         try {
31.             pageSize =Integer.parseInt(req.getParameter("pageSize"));
32.         } catch (NumberFormatException e) {
33.         }
34.         // 查询条件
35.         String stuname = req.getParameter("stuname");
36.         String stuage = req.getParameter("stuage");
37.         // 调用service层服务处理业务逻辑
38.         PageBean<Student> pageBean
    =studentService.findByPage(stuname,stuage,currentPage,pageSize);
39.         // 将数据放入请求域
40.         req.setAttribute("pageBean",pageBean);
41.         req.setAttribute("stuname", stuname);
42.         req.setAttribute("stuage", stuage);
43.         // 响应数据,页面跳转
44.         req.getRequestDispatcher("showStudent.jsp").forward(req,resp);
45.     }
46. }
